---
import BlogPostLayout from '../../layouts/BlogPostLayout.astro';
import { Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardDescription, CardContent } from '../../components/ui/card';
import { Button } from '../../components/ui/button';
import { Badge } from '../../components/ui/badge';
import { getBlogPost } from '../../lib/blog-posts';

// Export frontmatter for auto-discovery
export const frontmatter = {
  title: 'Longevity Hacks: Living to 100 with Peak Performance',
  description: 'Evidence-based strategies for healthspan extension',
  author: 'Dr. Lisa Martinez',
  date: '2025-01-15',
  topic: 'health' as const,
  tags: ['longevity', 'biohacking', 'nutrition', 'fitness', 'wellness'],
};

const post = getBlogPost('longevity-hacks')!;
---

<BlogPostLayout post={post}>
  <p class="text-lg">
    Living longer isn't just about adding years to your life—it's about adding life to your years. The latest research in longevity science reveals that our healthspan (years lived in good health) can be dramatically extended through evidence-based interventions that are accessible to everyone. Here's what the science actually says works.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 border-l-4 border-green-500 rounded-r-lg p-8 my-8">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">The Longevity Fundamentals</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-2">
          Before diving into advanced biohacking, master these core pillars that account for 80% of longevity outcomes:
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold">
            <span class="text-green-500">✓</span> Movement & Exercise
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold">
            <span class="text-green-500">✓</span> Nutrition & Diet
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold">
            <span class="text-green-500">✓</span> Sleep Quality
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold">
            <span class="text-green-500">✓</span> Stress Management
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold">
            <span class="text-green-500">✓</span> Social Connection
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold">
            <span class="text-green-500">✓</span> Purpose & Meaning
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Exercise: The Most Powerful Intervention</h2>

  <p class="mb-6">
    If there's one thing that comes closest to a "longevity pill," it's exercise. But not all exercise is created equal when it comes to extending healthspan.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <Card client:load className="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500/5 to-orange-500/5 border-l-4 border-l-red-500">
      <CardHeader>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
          <CardTitle className="text-xl">Zone 2 Cardio</CardTitle>
        </div>
        <CardDescription>The mitochondrial medicine</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p class="text-sm mb-4">
          Low-intensity aerobic exercise where you can still hold a conversation. Builds mitochondrial capacity and metabolic health.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 space-y-2">
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Frequency:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">4-5x per week</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Duration:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">45-60 minutes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Heart Rate:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">60-70% of max</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card client:load className="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/5 to-indigo-500/5 border-l-4 border-l-blue-500">
      <CardHeader>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
          </svg>
          <CardTitle className="text-xl">Strength Training</CardTitle>
        </div>
        <CardDescription>Muscle is longevity armor</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p class="text-sm mb-4">
          Resistance training maintains muscle mass, bone density, and metabolic health. Critical for preventing sarcopenia.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 space-y-2">
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Frequency:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">3-4x per week</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Duration:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">45-60 minutes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Focus:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">Full body, compound lifts</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card client:load className="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/5 to-pink-500/5 border-l-4 border-l-purple-500">
      <CardHeader>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
          <CardTitle className="text-xl">VO2 Max Training</CardTitle>
        </div>
        <CardDescription>High-intensity intervals</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p class="text-sm mb-4">
          Short bursts of all-out effort. VO2 max is one of the strongest predictors of all-cause mortality.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 space-y-2">
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Frequency:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">1-2x per week</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Protocol:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">4x4 min @ 90-95% max HR</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Recovery:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">3 min easy between sets</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card client:load className="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/5 to-teal-500/5 border-l-4 border-l-green-500">
      <CardHeader>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 10l-2 1m0 0l-2-1m2 1v2.5M20 7l-2 1m2-1l-2-1m2 1v2.5M14 4l-2-1-2 1M4 7l2-1M4 7l2 1M4 7v2.5M12 21l-2-1m2 1l2-1m-2 1v-2.5M6 18l-2-1v-2.5M18 18l2-1v-2.5" />
          </svg>
          <CardTitle className="text-xl">Stability & Mobility</CardTitle>
        </div>
        <CardDescription>Move well to move often</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p class="text-sm mb-4">
          Balance, flexibility, and movement quality prevent falls and injuries that derail longevity.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 space-y-2">
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Frequency:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">Daily practice</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Duration:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">10-15 minutes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
            <span class="font-semibold">Activities:</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground">Yoga, tai chi, stretching</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Nutrition: What the Science Actually Says</h2>

  <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">The Longevity Diet Principles</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Prioritize Protein</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">1.6-2.2g per kg body weight to maintain muscle mass as you age</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Eat the Rainbow</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Diverse polyphenols from colorful vegetables and fruits</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Omega-3 Fats</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">2-3g EPA/DHA daily from fish or supplements</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Minimize Ultra-Processed Foods</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Strong association with all-cause mortality</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Time-Restricted Eating</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">12-14 hour overnight fast supports autophagy</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Moderate Caloric Intake</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Avoid chronic overfeeding; slight deficit may extend lifespan</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Sleep: The Foundation of Recovery</h2>

  <p class="mb-6">
    Sleep is when your body repairs, consolidates memories, and clears metabolic waste. Chronic sleep deprivation accelerates aging and increases disease risk.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-8">
    <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-5">
      <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">7-9</div>
      <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1">Hours per night</div>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Optimal sleep duration for most adults</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-5">
      <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">65-68°F</div>
      <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1">Room temperature</div>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Cool environment promotes deeper sleep</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-5">
      <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">10pm-6am</div>
      <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1">Ideal sleep window</div>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Align with circadian rhythm</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-3 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Sleep Optimization Protocol</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-muted rounded-lg">
        <span class="text-primary font-bold">☀️</span>
        <div>
          <strong class="text-sm block mb-1">Morning: Get Bright Light</strong>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">10-30 min of sunlight within 1 hour of waking sets circadian rhythm</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-muted rounded-lg">
        <span class="text-primary font-bold">🌙</span>
        <div>
          <strong class="text-sm block mb-1">Evening: Dim the Lights</strong>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Reduce blue light 2-3 hours before bed to boost melatonin</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-muted rounded-lg">
        <span class="text-primary font-bold">🌡️</span>
        <div>
          <strong class="text-sm block mb-1">Temperature Drop</strong>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Hot shower 1-2 hours before bed; cool down triggers sleep</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-muted rounded-lg">
        <span class="text-primary font-bold">📵</span>
        <div>
          <strong class="text-sm block mb-1">Device-Free Bedroom</strong>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Keep phones and screens out of the bedroom entirely</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Stress Management & Mental Health</h2>

  <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <p class="mb-6">
      Chronic psychological stress accelerates cellular aging through multiple mechanisms including shortened telomeres, increased inflammation, and dysregulated cortisol. Managing stress isn't just about feeling better—it's about living longer.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-3">Evidence-Based Practices</h4>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <Badge client:load variant="secondary">Meditation</Badge>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">10-20 min daily reduces cortisol and inflammation</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <Badge client:load variant="secondary">Breathwork</Badge>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">5 min of 4-7-8 breathing activates parasympathetic system</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <Badge client:load variant="secondary">Nature Time</Badge>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">2 hours per week in nature significantly lowers stress</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <Badge client:load variant="secondary">Gratitude</Badge>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Daily journaling improves mental and physical health</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-3">Social Connection</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">
          Strong social relationships are one of the most robust predictors of longevity—on par with not smoking and more important than obesity or physical inactivity.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded-lg p-4">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Action Items:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs">
            <li>• Cultivate 3-5 close relationships</li>
            <li>• Join communities aligned with your values</li>
            <li>• Prioritize in-person connection over digital</li>
            <li>• Help others (volunteering boosts longevity)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Advanced Longevity Interventions</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <Card client:load>
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-lg">Supplements with Evidence</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>Consider after mastering the basics</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b">
            <span class="font-semibold">Omega-3 (EPA/DHA)</span>
            <Badge client:load variant="outline">Strong</Badge>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b">
            <span class="font-semibold">Vitamin D3</span>
            <Badge client:load variant="outline">Strong</Badge>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b">
            <span class="font-semibold">Magnesium</span>
            <Badge client:load variant="outline">Moderate</Badge>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b">
            <span class="font-semibold">Creatine</span>
            <Badge client:load variant="outline">Moderate</Badge>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b">
            <span class="font-semibold">NAD+ Precursors</span>
            <Badge client:load variant="outline">Emerging</Badge>
          </div>
        </div>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card client:load>
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-lg">Regular Health Monitoring</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>Track biomarkers that matter</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary">•</span>
            <span><strong>Lipid panel:</strong> ApoB, Lp(a), LDL-P (not just LDL-C)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary">•</span>
            <span><strong>Metabolic:</strong> Fasting glucose, insulin, HbA1c</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary">•</span>
            <span><strong>Inflammation:</strong> hsCRP, homocysteine</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary">•</span>
            <span><strong>Hormones:</strong> Thyroid, testosterone, cortisol</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary">•</span>
            <span><strong>Performance:</strong> VO2 max, grip strength, DEXA scan</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500/10 to-orange-500/10 border-l-4 border-amber-500 rounded-r-lg p-6 my-8">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">What NOT to Do</h3>
        <p class="mb-3">These behaviors dramatically accelerate aging:</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500">✗</span> Smoking (obvious but worth stating)
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500">✗</span> Chronic alcohol overconsumption
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500">✗</span> Sedentary lifestyle
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500">✗</span> Chronic sleep deprivation
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500">✗</span> Social isolation
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500">✗</span> Unmanaged chronic stress
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Your Longevity Action Plan</h2>

  <div class="space-y-4 my-8">
    <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">Start Here: The Essential Stack</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Month 1: Movement Foundation</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span>1.</span>
              <span>Walk 8,000+ steps daily</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span>2.</span>
              <span>Add 2-3 strength training sessions</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span>3.</span>
              <span>Start one 45-min Zone 2 cardio session</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Month 2: Recovery Optimization</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span>1.</span>
              <span>Establish consistent sleep schedule</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span>2.</span>
              <span>Implement sleep hygiene protocols</span>
            </li>
